CSRMESH_DATA_STREAM_FLUSH_T Struct Reference
CSRmesh&trade; » Models » Data Model

CSRmesh Data Model message types. More...

Data Fields

CsrUint16 streamsn
 Stream sequence number.
 

Detailed Description

Flushing Data: Upon receiving a DATA_STREAM_FLUSH message, the device saves the StreamSN field into the StreamSequenceNumber model state and responds with DATA_STREAM_RECEIVED with the StreamNESN field set to the value of the StreamSequenceNumber model state. The device also flushes all partially received stream data from this peer device.
